<emphasis box="[625,914,1740,1766]" italics="true" pageId="20" pageNumber="21">Rolland-Germain 28690</emphasis>
(lecto-, designated here: MT00132174!; isolecto-: MT00132175!). – Additional type material: 
<collectingCountry box="[899,990,1778,1804]" name="Canada" pageId="20" pageNumber="21">Canada</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingRegion box="[1006,1099,1778,1804]" country="Canada" name="Quebec" pageId="20" pageNumber="21">Quebec</collectingRegion>
, thickets and borders of woods, near mouth of Marsouin River (Gaspé Co.), 
<date box="[875,1029,1815,1841]" pageId="20" pageNumber="21" value="1922-07-26">26 Jul. 1922</date>
, 
<emphasis box="[1045,1206,1815,1841]" italics="true" pageId="20" pageNumber="21">M.L. Fernald</emphasis>
and 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="20" pageNumber="21">A.S. Pease 25014</emphasis>
(syn-: MT00206842!). – Note: Marie-Victorin &amp; Rousseau cited the two collections and mentioned that the type is in the herbarium of the Université de Montreal (MT). However, there are two specimens of 
<emphasis box="[444,619,1927,1952]" italics="true" pageId="20" pageNumber="21">Marie-Victorin</emphasis>
and 
<emphasis box="[674,960,1926,1952]" italics="true" pageId="20" pageNumber="21">
Rolland-Germain 
<quantity box="[887,960,1926,1952]" metricMagnitude="2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="7.28726" pageId="20" pageNumber="21" unit="in" value="28690.0">28690</quantity>
</emphasis>
