<emphasis box="[544,639,1963,1989]" italics="true" pageId="20" pageNumber="21">Fernald</emphasis>
and 
<emphasis box="[693,843,1964,1990]" italics="true" pageId="20" pageNumber="21">Pease 25014</emphasis>
(Geoffrey Hall, MT, pers. com.). The annotated specimen is here formally designated as 
<typeStatus box="[710,821,2001,2027]" pageId="20" pageNumber="21">lectotype</typeStatus>
.
</paragraph>
